name: Silverback
description:
The silverback gorilla of money clips.... here it is. Crushed aluminum look with carbon fiber strength. Take carbon fiber money clips to the next level with this unique Silverback money clip. 
 

Quality: Each money clip comes with a 5 year warranty against de-lamination. 

Security: The Silverback design blocks most RF signals that could capture your credit card data or other important personal information.
 
Nerd stuff: This clip is made with Texalium. Texalium was developed by a company based out of California named Hexcel. Itâ€™s a fiberglass-basic fabric that has a proprietary finish and a thin coating of aluminum on the surface. The aluminum coating is 99.99% pure and approximately 200 angstroms in thickness.
